    {
      "id": "3b21b5bd-64c8-498a-b8c4-db1ed95342f5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Learning Dashboards can be obtained from Adaptive Learning Platforms to provide an overview of student progress to the educator. Most ALP are evaluated on their ability to use data from multiple sources, their predictive performance but the effectiveness of the Learning Analytics Dashboards is something that is not as explored.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
